246 facility rates based on the cost reporting period endingended
247 June 30, 2020, the current asset value, as described in Rule
248 560-X-22-.14(11) of the Alabama Administrative Code, for each
249 nursing facility, after applying the July 1, 2020, rebasing as
250 provided under Rule 560-X-22-.14(11) of the Alabama
251 Administrative Code, used to calculate nursing facility rates,
252 shall be recalculated by adding to each respective nursing
